item.name: device-name
item.description: User defined device name. The POS should indicate the maximum supported string length. If the user entered string is too long, the device will store as much as possible and will return the <OKNearestLegal ValueSubstituted>.Additional information: The maximum supported string length is 32 characters. If the user entered string is too long, the device will store the first 32 characters and will return the <noError> status.
